Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.18,0:00:06.82,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去寻找吧 收集起梦的碎片{\fad(250,0)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.66,0:00:18.13,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使胸中苦闷 去感受真切的现在吧{\fad(0,400)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.67,0:00:22.77,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比外表更单纯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.47,0:00:26.31,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是却无法传达
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.14,0:00:33.88,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要说的话 总是藏在口袋里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.49,0:00:40.35,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充满孩子气的话语 如今已无法开口
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.83,0:00:48.39,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说时间会冲淡一切 我们却无法相互理解
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.39,0:00:54.62,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,24小时 一直相信着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.64,0:00:58.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.41,0:01:03.08,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使只是俗常的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.38,0:01:09.45,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间总是 微笑着匆匆流逝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.52,0:01:21.30,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起回忆 还是去追求理想的今天{\fad(0,1025)}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.79,0:22:17.29,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们 在生命的旅程中{\fad(400,0)}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.86,0:22:23.37,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渐渐地 失去所有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.80,0:22:29.18,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我仍坚信着 追逐着光明
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.81,0:22:36.35,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在与你 一同出发{\fad(0,1050)}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.19,0:22:46.39,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今在那深深的丛林中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.69,0:22:52.20,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也一定埋藏着 被丢弃的心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.53,0:22:58.70,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若能把握时光的轮回
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.70,0:23:05.21,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许 能再次飞翔{\fad(0,1050)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.35,0:23:13.62,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们将彷徨着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.15,0:23:20.06,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生存下去 直到永远
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.22,0:23:25.60,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍然坚信着 追逐着光明
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.03,0:23:32.60,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在与你 一同出发{\fad(0,1000)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.22,0:01:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 帮我拿酱油
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.12,0:01:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起来伸出手不就拿到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.58,0:02:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我就不用酱油了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.49,0:02:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦 怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.62,0:02:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这紧张兮兮的气氛是怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.93,0:02:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.80,0:02:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷不知道你在那边发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.80,0:02:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过难得大家一起吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.47,0:02:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不能开心一点嘛 怎么样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.07,0:02:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷 好冷哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.58,0:02:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.39,0:02:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子她妈 她到底是怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.49,0:02:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不着担心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.92,0:02:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看 茶叶梗立起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.72,0:02:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远隔万里而相通的二人之心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.13,0:02:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.10,0:02:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像已经好久没有来学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.61,0:02:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.94,0:02:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由加 绘理 步美 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.01,0:03:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你怎么还这么悠闲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.68,0:03:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大事不好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.69,0:03:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你得了economy class症候群请假的时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.69,0:03:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs23}economy class症候群：实际上不存在这种疾病
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.79,0:03:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么乱七八糟的症候群啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.56,0:03:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷又学会新的病名了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.50,0:03:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北条学长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.30,0:03:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.09,0:03:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.54,0:03:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.84,0:03:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩是一年级的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.84,0:03:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这段时间总是缠着北条同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.68,0:03:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北条同学好像也不是很讨厌她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.31,0:03:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办？戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.22,0:03:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么怎么办？这不是好事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.65,0:03:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.99,0:03:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放着不管可是会被抢走的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.49,0:03:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方才一年级
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.22,0:03:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮肤又这么光滑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.73,0:03:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是北条同学那样的男生最喜欢的类型哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.73,0:03:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我又没在跟北条同学交往
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.73,0:03:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.10,0:03:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然另外有男朋友对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:04:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.24,0:04:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.30,0:04:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么可能会表现得这么平静
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.05,0:04:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是谁嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.35,0:04:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.88,0:04:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从实招来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.38,0:04:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样啦 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.89,0:04:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我光是想起他就一肚子火
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.32,0:04:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.16,0:04:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.66,0:04:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快要上课了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.10,0:04:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要快点了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.73,0:04:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.43,0:04:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.30,0:04:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是烦死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.30,0:04:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.17,0:04:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在怀疑我什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.74,0:04:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你刚才一直是那样看我的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.45,0:04:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要冲我发脾气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.45,0:04:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是你自己有那种奇怪的误会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.12,0:04:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.19,0:04:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不想看到你这张脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.25,0:04:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便你去哪好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.19,0:04:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.46,0:04:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.39,0:04:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去钢牙那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.70,0:04:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是要回家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.13,0:04:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.53,0:05:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.71,0:05:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么看都只是一口古井而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.05,0:05:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里跟戈薇的国家连在一起的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.05,0:05:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是能通过古井的只有戈薇和犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.66,0:05:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明只有犬夜叉能去接戈薇回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.99,0:05:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只没大脑的笨狗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.56,0:05:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却不知道在赌什么气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.16,0:05:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是拿他没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.50,0:05:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.50,0:05:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定有人在背后说我坏话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.50,0:05:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉 有人说你坏话也不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.57,0:05:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你的确干了那么多蠢事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.24,0:05:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.25,0:05:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 老太婆 你说我做了什么蠢事啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.52,0:05:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋就是笨蛋 无可救药了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.95,0:05:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要找出四魂碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.02,0:05:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇的灵力是不可少的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.26,0:05:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你却搞不清楚状况
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.96,0:05:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还把她给气回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.19,0:05:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你少啰唆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.20,0:06:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是她自己擅自跑回去的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.03,0:06:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说什么“我要回家了 笨蛋”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.54,0:06:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.84,0:06:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.54,0:06:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你学戈薇一点都不像
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.41,0:06:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事情有什么所谓嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.98,0:06:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 请大家排好队
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.49,0:06:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 姑娘的手相不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.35,0:06:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以后会很长寿而且子孙满堂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.99,0:06:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法师大人 是真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.73,0:06:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.63,0:06:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你愿意为我生个孩子吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.43,0:06:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法师大人你好讨厌哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.30,0:06:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法师大人刚才也跟我说了一样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.50,0:06:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要看到美女
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.94,0:06:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就忍不住想要对方为我生孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.30,0:06:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 这么看来似乎有点苗头
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.74,0:06:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是不知道我能不能一次满足你们二位呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.33,0:06:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.01,0:06:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法师大人好讨厌哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.58,0:06:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是老头子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.09,0:07:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.09,0:07:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我们现在怎么急也没有用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.33,0:07:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除非犬夜叉能够好好冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.96,0:07:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则我们几个根本是无能为力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.75,0:07:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉笨得无可救药了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.17,0:07:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加上他的脾气又臭又硬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.10,0:07:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看是没希望了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.17,0:07:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.67,0:07:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后最好不要靠近枯井
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.28,0:07:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.48,0:07:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们想想犬夜叉的性格
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.18,0:07:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是发现有人在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.85,0:07:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算他想去接戈薇小姐也去不了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.12,0:07:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那家伙与表面相反
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.69,0:07:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内心也有很可爱的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.06,0:07:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人不可貌相啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.29,0:07:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们眼前就有个最好的例子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.14,0:07:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 没人在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.37,0:07:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇那家伙 我还是无法原谅她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.08,0:07:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对 要让她道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.71,0:08:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 这次你逃不掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.95,0:08:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.72,0:08:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在跟什么样的男生交往啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.72,0:08:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.22,0:08:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个小气的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.39,0:08:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野蛮任性又暴躁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.16,0:08:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还是个超～级醋坛子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.03,0:08:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是如果爱吃醋的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.16,0:08:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就表示他很喜欢戈薇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.03,0:08:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 原来很顺利嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.90,0:08:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为会更有趣点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.17,0:08:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不是很好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.47,0:08:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人对戈薇很专情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.91,0:08:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是这样的话我也没话说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.81,0:08:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙没办法忘记以前喜欢过的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.05,0:08:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都犹豫不决呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.55,0:08:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛 仔细想一想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.55,0:08:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉明明是喜欢桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.55,0:08:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要因为我吃醋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.39,0:08:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇受到了很猛烈的追求对不对？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.06,0:08:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人还想杀了接近我的男人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.43,0:08:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.23,0:08:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他到底是什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.07,0:08:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇 你为什么要跟那种人交往呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.34,0:08:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你必须跟他分手 绝对不能再见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.44,0:08:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.84,0:09:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是野蛮又任性吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.21,0:09:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还脚踏两条船
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.35,0:09:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然说如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.61,0:09:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可 可是他也有优点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.62,0:09:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人很温柔 而且很强大很可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.35,0:09:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.09,0:09:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该不会是喜欢他吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.09,0:09:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢…？我喜欢犬夜叉？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.60,0:09:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇一定是喜欢他的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.10,0:09:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.87,0:09:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢犬夜叉…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.25,0:09:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 她不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.49,0:09:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里…充满了戈薇的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.27,0:09:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.90,0:10:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还记得我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是戈薇姐姐的弟弟 叫草太
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.54,0:10:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是来玩的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.78,0:10:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.54,0:10:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.91,0:10:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你们没有吵架啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.15,0:10:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为姐姐看上去心情很不好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.65,0:10:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.92,0:10:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她还在生气啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.79,0:10:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个女人真爱计较
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.66,0:10:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 怎么突然觉得好累…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.03,0:10:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.84,0:10:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.94,0:10:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 狗狗哥哥他…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.31,0:10:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.31,0:10:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不要告诉戈薇我到这来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.68,0:10:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是男人之间的约定哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.05,0:10:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人之间的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.07,0:10:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.52,0:10:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草太？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.69,0:10:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回来啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.06,0:10:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么随便进别人的房间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.83,0:11:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…那个…这是男人之间的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.97,0:11:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过仔细想想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.58,0:11:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时犬夜叉这么辛苦跑来救我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.21,0:11:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我却站在钢牙那一边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.35,0:11:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…是我不对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.99,0:11:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.22,0:11:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.73,0:11:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不会向她道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.10,0:11:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.73,0:11:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙到底去干什么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.87,0:11:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个让人操心的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.11,0:11:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 弥勒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.61,0:11:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你自己说不准我们靠近枯井的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.58,0:11:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.75,0:11:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事情就是要观看过程才好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.42,0:12:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日暮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.39,0:12:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到学校里来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.26,0:12:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病已经好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.76,0:12:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电影？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.26,0:12:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们最近都没时间好好谈话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.63,0:12:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真伤脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.27,0:12:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这周的周末
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.27,0:12:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得应该回去比较好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.27,0:12:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你周六没空吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.91,0:12:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.54,0:12:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会去吧 戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.68,0:12:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说她想去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.15,0:12:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.05,0:12:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.62,0:12:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样 周六见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.79,0:12:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你们干嘛擅自帮我决定嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.79,0:12:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像北条同学这样正常的男人才适合戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.96,0:12:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.06,0:12:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续跟那个醋坛子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.06,0:12:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又花心 还有暴力倾向的男生交往下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.93,0:12:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇的将来会很悲惨的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.20,0:12:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是在说犬夜叉吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.30,0:12:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 你一定要去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.83,0:13:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉还在生气吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.20,0:13:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他本来就很顽固的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.83,0:13:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不想看到你那张脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.84,0:13:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊…现在回去的话可能又要吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.35,0:13:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为姐姐看上去心情很不好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.36,0:13:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.99,0:13:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…不要突然冒出来啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.00,0:13:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你赶紧去接她回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.86,0:13:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇会原谅你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.03,0:13:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你在胡说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.53,0:13:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那岂不是好像是我错了一样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.14,0:13:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来就是你不对！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.27,0:13:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还在怀疑戈薇是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.88,0:14:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还说要决斗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.25,0:14:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是那种时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.25,0:14:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢牙受伤了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.89,0:14:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇确实保护了钢牙让他逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.56,0:14:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明知道钢牙是犬夜叉的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.72,0:14:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且戈薇还不计较自己被他劫持并遇到危险
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.66,0:14:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 明明最受钢牙欺负的是戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.17,0:14:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么她还要帮钢牙啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.27,0:14:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.40,0:14:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇说不定真的喜欢上了钢牙对不对？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.91,0:14:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要问我！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.18,0:14:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要劝人家的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.31,0:14:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先想好一套说词再来行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.05,0:14:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在给我滚吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.19,0:14:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 犬夜叉 刚才是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.20,0:14:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.43,0:14:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死人了 你真的是很烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.57,0:15:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过不去接她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.70,0:15:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就绝对不会去接她！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.34,0:15:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 你先听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.57,0:15:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这种麻烦的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.58,0:15:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去找人生经验丰富的枫姥姥商量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.21,0:15:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是最好的办法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.35,0:15:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要你多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.62,0:15:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用担心 我不会说出你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.59,0:15:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就假装是要问我朋友的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.32,0:15:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.59,0:15:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.09,0:15:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.33,0:15:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是可以稍微听你一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.60,0:15:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.00,0:15:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 只…只是稍微哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.34,0:15:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实呢 我是帮我一个狗狗朋友来找你商量的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.37,0:15:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.84,0:15:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.98,0:15:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说 你那个狗朋友怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.61,0:15:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个狗狗啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.85,0:15:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢上一只猫咪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.35,0:15:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是没想到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.26,0:15:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了一匹野狼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.12,0:15:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且对猫咪一见钟情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.89,0:15:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.49,0:16:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狗狗与野狼每次见面都会打架
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.16,0:16:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.76,0:16:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野狼 从狗狗身边抢走了猫咪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.00,0:16:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是仇恨野狼的妖怪出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.34,0:16:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野狼受了重伤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.27,0:16:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后赶来救猫咪的狗狗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.64,0:16:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使消灭了妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.01,0:16:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狗狗想把受伤的野狼也一并收拾掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.15,0:16:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫咪却保护了野狼 让他逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.79,0:16:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫咪只是保护了受伤的野狼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.69,0:16:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狗狗却怀疑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.93,0:16:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫咪是不是喜欢上那只野狼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.03,0:16:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后猫咪就生气地回到了自己的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.80,0:16:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 事情大概就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.41,0:16:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要让狗狗和猫咪和好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.54,0:16:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么做才好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.18,0:16:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先狗要承认自己错了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.55,0:16:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.81,0:16:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你激动什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.88,0:16:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是在说七宝的狗朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.92,0:17:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你继续说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.09,0:17:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想 猫咪可能等狗狗去接她等得都不耐烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.96,0:17:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这两个人都误会了对方所以无法和好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.37,0:17:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先要让两个人见面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.04,0:17:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后再好好谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.91,0:17:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这应该是解决问题最快捷的方法了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.16,0:17:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 你还要在这边待多久？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.43,0:17:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 我不能在这里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.50,0:17:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在学业繁忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.43,0:17:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能总是跑去战国时代
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.90,0:17:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明就总是跑去那边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.57,0:17:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为犬夜叉会来带我回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.01,0:17:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可能已经不会来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.68,0:17:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么会知道那种事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.55,0:17:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.58,0:18:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是姐姐一直在生气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.55,0:18:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他才不来的啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.39,0:18:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我一直在生气…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.46,0:18:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天一早再起来念书吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.83,0:18:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在根本集中不了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.07,0:18:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被子好舒服…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.31,0:18:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那边根本就睡不舒服啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.61,0:18:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实也不会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.58,0:18:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉会替我值夜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.31,0:18:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在…他在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.70,0:18:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 睡着了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.93,0:18:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.34,0:18:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦话？她梦到我了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.01,0:19:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.01,0:19:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这臭丫头到底在做什么梦啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.42,0:19:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我记住！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.96,0:19:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闹钟不见了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.59,0:19:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.73,0:19:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…是犬夜叉？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.67,0:19:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他来过了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.64,0:19:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,急事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.78,0:19:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以周六不能陪你去看电影了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.62,0:19:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.05,0:19:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.82,0:19:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…还有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.89,0:19:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别介意我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.92,0:19:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟那个一年级的女孩子去看电影吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.13,0:19:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…那孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.66,0:19:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是挺喜欢北条同学的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.03,0:19:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日暮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.50,0:20:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真傻 原来你是在意那种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.17,0:20:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不打算跟别的女生交往
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.21,0:20:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.27,0:20:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我有点高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.41,0:20:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日暮原来因为我在吃醋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.65,0:20:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.28,0:20:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我下次再约你好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.18,0:20:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.42,0:20:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北条同学真坚强…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.19,0:20:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉也能像那样自信满满的就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.97,0:20:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈…戈薇？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.93,0:20:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.67,0:20:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正犬夜叉不会道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.34,0:20:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我稍微向他低头
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.74,0:20:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就能和好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.68,0:20:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.31,0:20:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.81,0:20:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那是什么表情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.72,0:20:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还在生气对不对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.12,0:20:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.82,0:20:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好高兴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.36,0:20:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到犬夜叉会这么老实地向我道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.89,0:20:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 真的不生气？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.70,0:21:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 你说是你不好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.46,0:21:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是因为你弄坏了这个闹钟？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.97,0:21:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然你以为还有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.97,0:21:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.64,0:21:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.14,0:21:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.11,0:21:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你们搞什么鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.25,0:21:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉其实是在反省的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.58,0:21:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还去了你那边两次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.22,0:21:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从戈薇走了以后 他就一直在叹气…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.15,0:21:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了两次？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.09,0:21:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你们不要多嘴啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.49,0:21:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 你们几个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.66,0:21:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么知道我去那边了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.89,0:21:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.13,0:21:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 既然已经回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.77,0:21:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就先老实道歉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.24,0:21:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少啰唆！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.57,0:21:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原谅我们吧 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.11,0:21:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不干呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.84,0:21:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也是担心你嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.31,0:21:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁要你们多管闲事！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.65,0:21:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可是在担心你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.25,0:21:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我必须要道歉啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.58,0:21:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就原谅他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.28,0:21:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真激动啊 因为他高兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.89,0:22:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为戈薇回来了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.69,0:22:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不是我的错！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.19,0:22:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样…风穴！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.29,0:22:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有本事就吸我进去！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.89,0:23:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感觉到有风
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.36,0:23:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥漫着妖气的风
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.80,0:23:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风突然成为利刃 将一切撕碎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.00,0:23:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在奈落的城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.94,0:23:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们发现了妖狼族的残骸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.54,0:24:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖狼族重新站起来 袭向犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.91,0:24:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手 钢牙 这是陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.65,0:24:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀死了你的同伴的不是犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.82,0:24:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.38,0:24:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被设计的死斗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.92,0:24:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬请期待
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.26,0:24:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉宝典
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.76,0:25:20.75,KEYPOINT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯真的少年 对戈薇一往情深{\pos(316,289)}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.76,0:25:20.75,KEYPOINT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送给她各种健康产品{\pos(288,414)}


